Title: A real options perspective on sequential acquisitions in China
Pages: 166-174
Author-Name: Dean Xu
Author-Workplace-Name: School of Business, The University of Hong Kong, Pokfulam, Hong Kong
Author-Name: Changhui Zhou
Author-Workplace-Name: Guanghua School of Management, Peking University, Beijing, China
Author-Name: Phillip H Phan
